    tags: [],
    excerpt: "Temporomandibular joint (TMJ) disorders can cause significant discomfort, from jaw pain and headaches to difficulty chewing and even earaches. If you\u2019re struggling with TMJ symptoms, you\u2019re not alone\u2014...",
